{"Id":808303,"Title":"三割股","Dynasty":"清","Author":"陈斌","Context":"初割股，为阿母。阿耶早去，惟阿母长寿。母曰嗟，三年疾久。他无长兄小弟，有良药焉求，良巫焉走。母视女心，女视母口。耶来掩母口，母勿呕。再割股，为老姑。老姑苏苏，顾妇呼儿疾，妇往扶。无儿无吾，思儿当反哺。儿负蓐，妇当代儿反哺。姑血枯，妇肉痡。妇无阿母惟吾姑。三割股，为夫苦。负疾如丘山，妾无疾心腐。天乎不可堕，姑何抚，娇儿何怙妾不苦。三割股，天乎不可堕。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"726526ec80187813fd06524b743ff44b","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5318394,"Sentence":"阿耶早去，惟阿母长寿。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"ā yē zǎo qù ，wéi ā mǔ cháng shòu ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5318396,"Sentence":"他无长兄小弟，有良药焉求，良巫焉走。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tā mó cháng xiōng xiǎo dì ，yǒu liáng yào yān qǐu ，liáng wū yān zǒu ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5318393,"Sentence":"初割股，为阿母。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chū gē gǔ ，wéi ā mǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5318395,"Sentence":"母曰嗟，三年疾久。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mǔ yuē jiē ，sān nián jǐ jiu ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5318397,"Sentence":"母视女心，女视母口。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mǔ shì nǚ xīn ，nǚ shì mǔ kǒu ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5318398,"Sentence":"耶来掩母口，母勿呕。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yē lái yǎn mǔ kǒu ，mǔ wù ǒu ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5318399,"Sentence":"再割股，为老姑。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zài gē gǔ ，wéi lǎo gū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5318400,"Sentence":"老姑苏苏，顾妇呼儿疾，妇往扶。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lǎo gū sū sū ，gù fù hū ér jǐ ，fù wǎng fú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5318401,"Sentence":"无儿无吾，思儿当反哺。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mó ér mó wú ，sāi ér dāng fǎn bǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"清"